box.php" file</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Version 1.4.2 - Released: Mar 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.3.5 support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Version 1.4.1 - Released: 02-19-2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Wordpress 4.1.1 Support</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Mini Search bug</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Version 1.4.0 - Released: 02-17-2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.3.0 sup</li>\n    <li>Added: Yith Woocommerce Wishlist 2.0 *note you must remove embedded wishlist to use it.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Version 1.3.5 - Released: 02-02-2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.2.11 support</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.4 - Released: 12-03-2014</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.2.8 support</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Duplicated og tag with Wordpress Seo plugin</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Image.php issue with W3 Total Cache plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.3 - Released: 10-15-2014</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.2.6 support</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.2 - Released: 10-08-2014</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Fixed: Product back flip issue</li>\n    <li>Fixed: "The settings of this image size have been disabled because its values are being overwritten by a filter." because of new WooCommerce 2.2.x</li>\n    <li>Fixed: YIW links problem</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.1 - Released: 09-17-2014</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.2.3 support</li>\n    <li>Added: Shotcode [line]</li>\n    <li>Fixed: ie version detect function</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Rich Snippet metadata</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Wishlist compatibility</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Cart Layout</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Toggle Menu on shop page</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Products cross sell wrong position on cat page</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Firefox and double spinner for number field</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Class Font error, prevent undefined index</li>\n    <li>Removed: Custom post type tags from wpml-config.xml</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 - Released: 03-25-2014</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Fixed: Empty line before php tag on top of the file.</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Product slider visual bug</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Shipping - Billing fields style</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.0 - Released: 02-18-2014</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Compatibility to Woocommerce 2.1.2</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Wrong Marketplace</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 - Released: 01-07-2014</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to WP 3.8</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 - Released: 12-04-2013</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Fixed: Various Bug</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released: 10-11-2013</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial theme version.</li>\n</ul>\n]]>\n	</changelog>\n</notifier>\n', 'yes'),
